    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/4731b890161735afab61c8cddf2da9df.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=800 height=65 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/4731b890161735afab61c8cddf2da9df.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong><i><u>Tagged</u></i></strong>》是一款真正的第一人称生存恐怖游戏，你将以涂鸦艺术家的身份穿越山村。在木棚、岩壁或其他结构上留下你的“涂鸦标记”，并祈祷当地人欣赏它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在涂鸦文化中，“标签”或“涂鸦”是指艺术家的艺术签名或原创作品。主要依赖艺术中的可读性和流畅性。你将在游戏中尝试喷洒涂鸦标签。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/ecead64971d8c8f4920136c773cdc77c.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=570 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/ecead64971d8c8f4920136c773cdc77c.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/ecead64971d8c8f4920136c773cdc77c.mp4?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/bdc42277105a58adf2fb76554c12611d.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=800 height=65 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/bdc42277105a58adf2fb76554c12611d.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Tagged</strong>》的背景是一座乡村山村，充满着令人不安的平静氛围。这是表达你艺术情感的完美温床。黑暗、红细胞光滑的流动、毛孔皮肤的哑光质感。灵感简直源源不断。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/5357bd9d2a7f5cdd85946d9767e17dbe.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=570 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/5357bd9d2a7f5cdd85946d9767e17dbe.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/5357bd9d2a7f5cdd85946d9767e17dbe.mp4?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/42cbbf41ca56726d97b7aeca26d8d567.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=800 height=65 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/42cbbf41ca56726d97b7aeca26d8d567.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于艺术家来说，呆在一个地方不是常见的做法，无论是身体上还是精神上。躲藏也是很奇怪的行为。大多数右脑主导的人经常四处走动，所以呆在一个地方实际上会让你更加显眼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/65aaa303ac662925fc33a608a2bb784c.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=570 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/65aaa303ac662925fc33a608a2bb784c.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/65aaa303ac662925fc33a608a2bb784c.mp4?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/c9f0066d6d48c869ded505e7b8a0c28a.poster.avif?t=1730746181\" width=800 height=65 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177330/extras/c9f0066d6d48c869ded505e7b8a0c28a.webm?t=1730746181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实的第一人称体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逼真的图形</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可映射的输入键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >字幕</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成后的小游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义图形设置</p></li></ul>",
